===Noun===
'''pirate''' (plural: [[pirates]])

# one who [[rob]]s ships while at sea; a [[nautical]] [[bandit]]
# (''internet'') one who reproduces [[copyright]]ed works without [[permission]] for the purpose of [[distributing]] them to others for free

===Verb===

# {''internet'') to attain an [[unauthorized copy]] of [[software]] or other works
#:''This evening I pirated a new computer game''

